cn:association.cn:title: Rapid Update - An outlook for U.S. GDP
cn:association.cn:shorterHeadline: Rapid Update - An outlook for U.S. GDP
cn:association.description: CNBC Rapid Update will offer new measures of how much an economic report changes the outlook on Wall Street for US growth forecasts.
cn:association.cn:linkHeadline: Rapid Update - An outlook for U.S. GDP
cn:association.headline: Rapid Update - An outlook for U.S. GDP
cn:association.cn:bodyTeaser:
CNBC Rapid Update offers a new measure for how much an economic report changes the outlook on Wall Street for US growth forecasts. With each major report that impacts Gross Domestic Product, Moody's Analytics and CNBC measure how much the n

ew data changes the average tracking forecast among a select group of Wall Street economists. A tracking forecast is an estimate for GDP that changes that changes with incoming data.

Updated: May 16, 2018
